Good Night Inns are part of The Great British Pub Card. Good Night Inns are a collection of charming hotels with heaps of character. Our 43 hotels – located all across the country – all have their own individual story, traditions and heritage. The Great British Pub Card is the leading pub gift card that can be redeemed against food, drink or accommodation in over 3000 locations nationwide. Including brands such as Chef & Brewer, Loch Fyne, Flaming Grill, Hungry Horse and many others. The Great British Pub Card is also available to purchase as a digital code, its flexible and offers a vast choice of food, drink or dining opportunities. Perfect for celebrating those special times with family, catching-up with friends or meeting with colleagues. For more information visit www.greatbritishpubcard.co.uk.